titles.title: Directing the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make a technical correction in the enrollment of the bill H.R. 3194.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on House Administration.
Mr. Pease asked unanimous consent to discharge from committee and consider.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

vote.text: Received in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Unanimous Consent.

action.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.

bill.summary: 11/19/1999--Introduced. Directs the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make a technical correction in the enrollment of H.R. 3194 (District of Columbia appropriations).
